sequenceDiagram
    participant Config
    participant API
    participant Parser as Dedicated MT5 Structure Parser
    participant Meta
    participant Time
    participant Env
    participant Handoff

    Config->>Config: Resolve MT5 schema + dedicated parser
    API->>Parser: MT5 input view
    Parser-->>Env: Parsed MT5 structure view
    Meta-->>Env: Prepared metadata
    Time-->>Env: Stabilized timestamp
    Env->>Handoff: Handoff contract
